productItem.name: BCG Men's Basic 5" Running Short

value: 2 side pockets and 1 inner key pocket
Machine wash cold with like colors, do not bleach, do not use softeners; tumble dry low, do not iron, do not dry clean
Made of 86% polyester and 14% spandex for sporty wear
Reflective, heat-transferred BCG™ logo helps keep you visible and safe during low-light runs
Drawstring closure and an elastic waistband
Moisture-wicking Tru-Wick™ fabric technology and an odor-resistant finish help keep you feeling fresh

productItem.longDescription: The BCG Men's Basic 5" Running Short is made of polyester and spandex and features a reflective, heat-transferred BCG™ logo to help keep you visible and safe during low-light runs. The Tru-Wick™ fabric technology and polyester inner brief help you stay dry and comfortable. Drawstring closure. 5-inch inseam.
